Ugle, I considered using my O2 for a mail server, but I'd heard that there were security issues on Irix, plus I'm not really using the NT box for anything except a web and DNS server, so I figured I might as well have it do all the work. I don't have Linux installed yet, and when I do the machine it will be on will frequently be swapping back and forth with Win98, so there's likely to be many hours or even days when it won't be running Linux.<br>
<br>
